data.description: Contract Fail. Back on the market. Great Investment. Great price allows new owner to update and have immediate equity. Low maintenance brick & vinyl exterior. 3BR and 2BA Down. 1BR and 1BA Up. Stainless Microwave & Dishwasher. Tile in Kitchen. Big inviting family room with fireplace. Mostly laminate/wood flooring down. Ceiling Fans. Nice sunroom. Laundry room. Fenced backyard. Home sold "as is". Good condition, but some cosmetic needed.
